Popular Nollywood actor, Samuel Alabi Oludayo Akinpelu, popularly known as Alabi Yellow is dead. It was learnt that the actor died earlier on Sunday in his home in Ikorodu, Lagos, PM News reports. He died at the age of 62 . The deceased was said to have suffered stroke after his wife’s death in March. However, popular philanthropist, Reverend Esther Ajayi alongside other actors rallied round to raise funds to cater for him. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.